      %table{ :cellspacing => "0", :border => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :width => "414" }
        - if Date.today > Date.new(2010,4,1)
          %tr
            %td{ :bgcolor => "#45331A" }
              %img{ :src => "images/img_pics/pic_gwendolyn_hp.jpg", :height => "284", :alt => "", :width => "414" }
          %tr
            %td#note
              %p
                %img{ :src => "images/img_headings/h_ourmission.gif", :height => "26", :alt => "Our Mission", :width => "137" }
              The Gwendolyn Strong Foundation (GSF) seeks to raise awareness about and fund research for Spinal Muscular Atrophy (SMA), the leading genetic killer of young children, and support those impacted by SMA and other life-altering diseases.
        - else
          %tr
            %td{ :bgcolor => "#45331A" }
              = link_to image_tag("img_misc/hp_chase.png", :border => "0", :alt => "Chase Community Giving and Gwendolyn Strong Foundation"), page_chase_path
