                %br
                The Gwendolyn Strong Foundation (GSF) was humbled to be voted #6 out of more than 500,000 organizations in the 2010 Chase Community Giving campaign on Facebook. For that honor, GSF received a $100,000 grant from Chase...
              %p
                %br
                = link_to "Click to learn more...", page_chase_path

